                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9851" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1117</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">788 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破茧成蝶：乐凡信息的“专精特新”小巨人跃迁之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Emerging as a Butterfly from a Cocoon: The Transformation Journey of Livefan Company, a “Little Giant” Firm</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邢蕊，王国红，王梦瑶，徐雅轩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市乐凡信息科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第二曲线；国产替代；专精特新“小巨人”企业；企业成长；乐凡公司；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">the second curve; domestic substitution; &quot;little giant&quot; firm; firm growth; Livefan company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乐凡公司是一家国家级专精特新小巨人企业。本案例重点描述了乐凡以消费电子产品起步，通过持续创新和战略转型，成功实现跨越式发展的创业历程。在国家提倡信创产业国产化替代以及推动中小型企业发展的背景下，乐凡响应政策号召，主动拥抱国产化转型，在医疗、工业互联网等信创产业领域构建起安全可控的技术体系，并实现国产芯片与操作系统的自主适配。通过本案例学习，让学生掌握第二曲线的基本概念与特点，理解第二曲线的必要性和内在驱动力，了解企业如何寻找并发展自己的第二曲线，实现企业生命周期的跨越。让学生理解以乐凡为代表的中小型企业国产化替代转型，对国家产业链安全和科技自立自强的战略意义。同时，案例中展现了新时代企业家的使命担当，有助于增强学生的科技报国意识和创新驱动发展意识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Livefan is a national-level “little giant” firm. This case focuses on Livefan&#39;s entrepreneurial journey, starting from consumer electronics, achieving leapfrog development through continuous innovation and strategic transformation. Against the backdrop of the national promotion of domestically developed information technology innovation industry, Livefan responded to the policy call, proactively embraced domestic substitution transformation, and established a secure and controllable technology system in the Information technology application innovation industry fields such as medical care and industrial internet, achieving independent adaptation of domestic chips and operating systems. Through the study of this case, students can master the basic concepts and characteristics of the second curve, understand the necessity and internal driving force of the second curve, and learn how enterprises can identify and develop their own second curves to achieve a leap in the enterprise life cycle. It also enables students to understand the strategic significance of the domestic substitution transformation of small and medium-sized enterprises represented by Livefan for the security of the national industrial chain and the self-reliance of science and technology. At the same time, the case showcases the mission and responsibility of entrepreneurs in the new era, which helps to enhance students&#39; awareness of serving the country through science and technology and innovation-driven development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）第二曲线理论的基本内容；（2）第一曲线与第二曲线的关系；（3）开启第二曲线的最佳时机和条件；（4）第二曲线的发展过程；（5）第二曲线创新的实现过程。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
